{
  "stem": "3848.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where we stayed while we were working to build a railroad that goes all around Moscow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just digging, bringing earth, putting up rails, and making the-- the-- the station.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We made it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on that rail, it was called [NON-ENGLISH], which I suppose is still in existence today-- that's all to protect the city of Moscow.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were cruising around Moscow with guns, the soldiers and everything, just to protect shooting at-- at the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the Germans were very close by that railroad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were 12 kilometers from Moscow when I was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they came, and they destroyed this rail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We fixed it again, and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After we got through fixing this railroad, they had no work for us anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they decided to send us to Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I found out that the whole transport is going to Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was at the end of 1941.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was already cold, winter in Moscow is pretty cold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I asked another few guys that were with me on the railroad whether they would like to go deeper into Russia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In order for us to go someplace, we didn't know where-- which transport goes where.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I was out on the station, I saw that the-- the cars from the Moscow underground, the metro, which I recognized, were standing outside.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I figured these cars, which were very precious to the Russians, were going to go somewhere deep into Russia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we decided, this group, to join this particular train and we traveled.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rather than to go to Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, I didn't know what Stalingrad meant, which I found out later what Stalingrad meant.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we decided to go deeper into Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
